    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>The BumbleBee Foundation</h1>
        <p>Changing the world, one step at a time</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <div>
            <a href="~/">Home</a>
            <a href="~/Home/About">About Us</a>
            <a href="~/Home/Projects">Projects</a>
            <a href="~/Home/Donations">Donations</a>
            <a href="~/Home/GetInvolved">Get Involved</a>
            <a href="~/Home/Contact">Contact Us</a>
            <a href="~/Home/DonorDashboard">Dashboard</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero">
        <h2>Making a Difference Together</h2>
        <p>Join us in our mission to improve lives worldwide.</p>
        <div class="button-container">
            <button onclick="window.location.href='/Register/Register'">Sign Up</button>
            <button onclick="window.location.href='/Register/Login'">Login</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="column">
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>We aim to empower communities through sustainable development projects.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
            <h3>Latest Projects</h3>
            <p>Discover our recent efforts in education, healthcare, and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
            <h3>Get Involved</h3>
            <p>Learn how you can contribute to our cause and make an impact.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
